<module>
    <h>àrd</h>
    <p><g>àrd</g>
        <en>high, tall</en> is a <a href="?xx=adjectives/simple_adjectives">simple
        adjective</a>.</p>

    <section>
        <h>nouns</h>
        <p><g>àrd</g> can have a <a href="?xx=nouns/common_nouns">common noun</a> as (deep)
            subject.</p>
        <module id="balla_aard">
            <h>balla àrd</h>
            <p><g><a href="?gd=balla">balla</a> àrd</g>
                <en>a high wall</en> – <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>A bheil am balla àrd? Tha.</gd>
                        <tr>Is the wall high? Yes, it is.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 20</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl>
            </p>
        </module>
        <module id="cnoc_aard">
            <h>cnoc àrd</h>
            <p><g><a href="?gd=cnoc">cnoc</a> àrd</g>
                <en>a tall hill</en> – <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Tha an cnoc seo àrd.</gd>
                        <tr>This hill is high.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 20</ref>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Càit a bheil an taigh mór? Tha an taigh mór air a’ chnoc
                            àrd.</gd>
                        <tr>Where is the big house? The big house is on the tall hill.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 21 [229]</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl>
            </p>
        </module>
    </section>





